body_html: @janstrelka : Assuming your issue is the same as what was talked about in #18530 then this means that the CPU you're running on does not support AVX instructions. Since TensorFlow 1.6, the release binaries require CPUs with AVX support. For older CPUs, you'll have to either build from source or use binaries built by others in the community (e.g. https://github.com/yaroslavvb/tensorflow-community-wheels )
